{
  "texts": [
    "However, in Interactive experiences, Room scale is the most frequently used, as it requires less movement.",
    "The endings of these experiences are usually Free, although in cases with more interaction, the endings tend to be Task-related.",
    "Currently, the most widely used are 6DoF 360° external tracking Desktop HMDs.",
    "However, it is expected that in the future, there will be a shift towards 6DoF internal tracking desktop and standalone HMDs.",
    "As these experiences gain complexity and interaction, it is more common to find elements such as characters, audio, and interface."
  ]
}